snippet.title: Bill Nye VS Kent Hovind - Short Creation Debate

localized.description:
Bill Nye VS Kent Hovind - Short Creation Debate

Kent Hovind is currently in prison for giving thousands of debates and lectures against the teaching of evolution and for exposing the "New World Order" to millions of Americans and people around the world.

UPDATE: KENT HAS BEEN RELEASED FROM PRISON! WATCH OUT EVOLUTIONISTS!
